  "description": "<p>📍 Singapore | Full-Time | Fresh Grads Welcome</p><p>Just graduated and unsure where to start? Royal Organisation provides <strong>hands-on training, mentorship, and real career exposure</strong> for fresh graduates.</p><p>No prior experience needed — we focus on attitude, willingness to learn, and growth potential.</p><p><strong>Ideal for:</strong> Fresh graduates seeking real-world experience and career clarity.<br /><br /><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul><li>🎓 Early-career individuals</li><li>📚 Willingness to learn and grow</li><li>😊 Positive attitude and strong commitment</li></ul><p><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p><ul><li>🧑‍🏫 Learn sales & marketing fundamentals</li><li>🎪 Support live event campaigns</li><li>📈 Build practical, real-world experience</li></ul><p><strong>What You’ll Gain</strong></p><ul><li>🎓 Hands-on sales industry training</li><li>🤝 1-on-1 mentorship</li><li>🚀 Clear career direction and growth</li><li>🌍 Travelling opportunities</li></ul>",
